headline: 2 Reasons to Like LRCX (and 1 Not So Much)
summary: Over the past six months, Lam Research’s shares (currently trading at $74.44) have posted a disappointing 8.8% loss while the S&P 500 was down 1.4%. This may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
